Sales_funnel_results.md

## Key Findings

- Overall conversion rate: 16.52%
- Largest drop-off occurred between Page View and Add to Cart.
- Payment completion rate was 91.88%.

### Recommendation

Improve product pages, customer reviews, and calls to action to increase Add-to-Cart conversions.

Traffic_source_results.md

## Key Findings

- Email Marketing Delivered the Highest Conversion Rate
- Organic Search Generated the Highest Website Traffic
- Paid Advertising Performed Well
- Social Media Had the Weakest Performance


### Recommendation
Increase Investment in Email Marketing, Optimize Organic Search Landing Pages, Continue Refining Paid Advertising
Reevaluate Social Media Strategy, Allocate Marketing Budget Based on Performance

Customer_journey_results.md

## Key Findings
- Average View-to-Cart Time: 11.16 minutes
- Customers Spend Slightly Longer Completing Their Purchase
- Average Cart-to-Purchase Time: 13.47 minutes
- The Average Purchase Journey Takes Less Than 25 Minutes
- Average Total Journey: 24.63 minutes

### Recommendation

Optimize Product Pages
Use high-quality product images.
Improve product descriptions.
Display customer reviews and ratings.
Highlight key benefits and promotions.
Make the "Add to Cart" button more prominent.
Simplify the Checkout Process
Autofill shipping and billing information where possible.
Offer multiple secure payment options.
Clearly display shipping costs and delivery estimates early in the checkout process.
end abandoned cart reminders within 30–60 minutes after a customer leaves without purchasing.
Display limited-time offers during the first hour after cart abandonment.
Use retargeting ads shortly after a customer exits the site.

Revenue_results.md

## Key Findings

- Strong Revenue Generation
- The website attracted 5,000 visitors.
- 826 visitors completed a purchase.
- Total revenue generated was $87,975.11.
- Average Order Value (AOV): $106.51
- Revenue per Visitor: $17.60

### Recommendation
Recommend complementary products at checkout ("Frequently Bought Together").
Create product bundles or multi-buy discounts.
Offer free shipping above a spending threshold.
Upsell premium products or extended warranties where appropriate.
aunch loyalty or rewards programs.
Send personalized post-purchase email campaigns.
Offer exclusive discounts to returning customers.
Recommend products based on previous purchases.



